lead_paragraph: If he really wants the once-again vacant England job Arsene Wenger's Arsenal players provided the Frenchman the perfect showreel in a classy 2-0 defeat of FC Basel to move joint top of Champions League Group A on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Dazzling Arsenal Raise Wenger's England Stock
